{"tid":1668272,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔不如出官方連狗同連豬毛公仔幫補營運？和理非遊行嗰陣人人帶住","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T16:48:17.000Z","uid":157304,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8889abd6af901bf6c91e0830d46799f6662cd439","tid":1668272,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"次次和理非遊行集會都見好多人帶pepe公仔一齊去，又幫佢打扮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家連豬連狗已成香港人衝出國際icon，貼到成街都係<br />\n加上你停咗廣告咁耐<br />\n如果你肯出公仔嚟支持營運<br />\n我相信連登仔女一定會買爆嚟支持你，帶晒出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔會鬧你食人血<br />\n<br />\n推到連仔見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aaddeddcb9debb0e1ae38a9f826713241eb42e","tid":1668272,"uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:56:03.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地<br />\n前晚開po到而家都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單野新鮮滾熱辣 connect全世界<br />\n依家就係最好時機！<br />\n<br />\n我地fight for freedom<br />\n我無宗教信仰 但我有宗教自由 <br />\n<br />\n早喺六月已經有宗教俾popo當眾侮辱 <br />\n打壓宗教自由之餘亦都對各個宗教不尊重<br />\n<br />\n睇原po！<br />\n既然我哋係fight for freedom<br />\n我咁更加係時候聲援我被打壓宗教自由嘅人！<br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d59659f020881dbc6a2f4bbcfdb0b24b9d036d7","tid":1668272,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186614580ee3c86cdfe546dd1c3a0c25a4d94c72","tid":1668272,"uid":2210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=